# Another Good Decision You Made

## Static atmospheric PNG backgrounds

This is underrated.

A lot of systems chase:

* over-animation
* excessive particle effects
* motion overload

But cinematic static compositions:

* load faster
* look more premium
* feel intentional
* scale better across devices
* create stronger atmosphere

Especially with:

* glass overlays
* subtle lighting
* restrained neon

That direction fits the “premium interactive mystery” identity much better than chaotic cyberpunk clutter.

